Prof Rwigamba [[File:Pro.-Dr-RWIGAMBA-Balinda.jpg|Pro.-Dr-RWIGAMBA-Balinda]]

Prof Rwigamba Balinda yavutse mu mwaka wi 1948 avukira muri kivu yaruguru ahitwa [[Kongo|masisi]] mu cyahoze ari [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Zaire]]

ubu akaba ari [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Repuburika iharanira Demokarasi ya Cong]]<nowiki/>o<ref>https://ar.umuseke.rw/soma-imibereho-ya-prof-rwigamba-balinda-umuyobozi-wa-ulk.hmtl</ref> akaba ari umuyobozi w'ikirenga

wa [[Kigali Independent University|Kaminuza yigenga ya Kigal]]<nowiki/>i iherereye i [[Kigali]] mu murenge wa Gisozi ndetse akaba ari nawe nyirayo

ya yishinze mu mwaka wi 1996 nyuma ya [[Genocide mu Rwanda|Genocide]] ya korewe abatutsi mu Rwanda mu 1994

== Amashuri yize ==
ahagana mu mwaka wi 1974 nibwo yarangije Lisence yambere  muri philosophie Anglaise muri kaminza imwe 

[[Kongo|y'Ikinshasa]] mumwaka wi 1977 kandi abona indi Lisence muri Linguistique Africaine muri [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|Kaminuza]] yi <ref>https://web.facebook.com/ulk.ac.rw/photos/prof-dr-rwigamba-balinda-founder-and-president-of-ulk/2425676364140102/?_rdc=1&_rdr</ref>

[[Kongo|Lubumbashi]] mu mwaka wi 1982 yabonye kandi impamya bushobozi yo kurwego rwa [[PDF|PHD]] arinabwo yabaga 

umuyobozi wa Kaminuza i [[Congo Brazzaville|Lubumbashi]] kubera uburyo yize ari umuhanga kandi abona amanota meza 

yigishije kandi no kuriyo kaminuza yigagaho. ndetse akaba yaranditse nibitabo byinshi bitandukanye<ref>https://rushyashya.net/prof-dr-rwigamba-balinda-yamuritse-agatabo-umukristo-wukuri/</ref>

